\s TUNAKIMBILIA UZURI WAKO
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Tunakimbila uzuri wako Bwana wangu, sawa ndege amkiavyo asubuhi, twapaza sauti yetu tukisema, Mungu wetu tusikilize daima.\bd*
\pc \bdit Moyo hunyenyekea, O’Mungu wangu, nita\bdit*\bdit kuimbia kwa sauti yangu yote ./.\bdit*\bdit Huo ndio uzima wangu./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Tunakimbilia utukufu wako Baba Mungu, shabaa yetu tunataka kufanana nawe, tunakimbilia uso wako Baba Mungu, utujalie utujaze nguvu zako.\bd*
\pc \bdit Moyo hunyenyekea, O’Mungu wangu, nitakuimbia kwa sauti yangu yote ./.Huo ndio uzima wangu./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Tunakimbilia mikono yako Bwana Mungu, tushike mikono tusije tukatereze, tunakuletea unyonge wetu Bwana Mungu, utujalie utujaze nguvu zako.\bd*
\pc \bdit Moyo hunyenyekea, O’Mungu wangu, nitakuimbia kwa sauti yangu yote ./.Huo ndio uzima wangu./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Tunakuletea upumbavu wetu Bwana Mungu, utujalie utujaze hekima yako, tunakuleteya kiburi chetu Bwana Yesu, utujaze unyenyekevu wako.\bd*
\pc \bdit Moyo hunyenyekea, O’Mungu wangu, nitakuimbia kwa sauti yangu yote ./.Huo ndio uzima wangu./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Furaha gani kukuona kati yetu Bwana, ni kama nyumba ilio na mwamba, furaha gani kukuona ndani yetu Bwana, ni furaha na raha zaidi.\bd*
\pc \bdit Moyo hunyenyekea, O’Mungu wangu, nitakuimbia kwa sauti yangu yote ./.Huo ndio uzima wangu./.\bdit*
